The 66th British Academy Film Awards are held in London with Argo winning best film, Ben Affleck winning best director and Daniel Day-Lewis and Emmanuelle Riva winning best actor and actress. (The Guardian) (Sky News Australia)Pat Kenny, most recently presenter of The Frontline, makes his return as host of The Late Late Show after the death this week of regular host Ryan Tubridy's father. (Irish Independent) (The Irish Times)